    <div class="col-xs-12 half-spaced">
      <p><b>This Privacy Statement applies to "PipeCandy.com" owned and operated by PipeCandy Inc. doing business as "PipeCandy". At PipeCandy, your privacy is always at the top of our priorities, and we are focused on protecting it from unauthorized access.</b></p>
